latestPosts.caption:
Happy 14th birthday to the little human who made me feel both old and young at the same time! With a Huge age gap between us but somehow you’re still the bossy one. Watching you grow up has been the sweetest (and funniest) ride. Love you, mini-me with extra sass!” though you’re not such a baby anymore. It feels like just yesterday I was holding you in my arms, and now you’re growing into this beautiful and strong young woman. We may be 15 years apart, but you’ve taught me so much about new generational stuff,trends, trending songs and patience (a lot of patience!). I’m so proud of the person you’re becoming. Keep shining, little one—you’ve always had a piece of my heart.”
❤️ I love you 🫶
